staff_statistics.description_chinese: Big note on you help group stay safe and go ahead. Party watch all. Every action show your care for future.
staff_statistics.footer: You act. It helps OP-FW grow. OP-Framework good and steady. Your work is seen. We all move forward. Team help brings success. Hard work makes great things. Glory to OP-FW!
staff_statistics.footer_chinese: Every move show you loyal to Party. You stay true. System eyes watch. Your work is logged and praised as our big progress. Obedience keeps peace. Watchfulness brings plenty. Glory to CCP!
staff_statistics.level_0_description: You walk staff path. Power lies sleep. You learn from mentors. You watch realm energies swirl with curiosity. Seeds of greatness inside you. They wait for you to step forward and grab them.
staff_statistics.level_10_description: Legends tell of your rise. You become a light that calms storms. The glow of your staff energy shines everywhere, making unity strong among those you guard. At the peak of mortal power, you shape the realm with firm decrees.
staff_statistics.level_1_description: Finally, first spark of staff magic shines in your hands. It guides how you answer to small server trouble. You ready to calm quarrel here and there, quiet unrest. You want prove you worth. The arcane bond grows strong with every call for help, light of higher mastery.
staff_statistics.level_2_description: Take the subtle currents that shape the server. You juggle reports and punishment steps with new skill. Chaos trembles, but your calm face and fast fixes keep peace. Each move weaves you deeper into the realmâ€™s cloth, making you strong to guard harmony.
staff_statistics.level_3_description: Your command of wards and banish spells keeps the server calm. Trouble makers find they fail before your watch, and your glowing staff stands as sign of power. Even in dark, your steady drive turns trouble into win.
staff_statistics.level_4_description: From the darkest corners, you stand guard, feeling the faintest mischief that threats the realm. Quick retributions and precise interventions show you as strong guardian, so no foe lingers long in your domain. The line between order and chaos stays safe under your eyes.
staff_statistics.level_5_description: Stars guide your judgments, giving you power to keep harmony with space grace. The realm looks to you for fair rules, trusting you to calm fights and lift those in need. Each day, your mastery of astral energy grows, lighting the way for staff and players alike.
staff_statistics.level_6_description: Your staff has big power. It banishes bad spirits fast. Fear runs wild among wild folk when your name is spoken, they know your anger hits all who upset the realm. With such power, you still seek fair justice, quick and sure.
staff_statistics.level_7_description: You shine with holy force. You lead the realmâ€™s guards and stop trouble before it starts. Whispers of your deeds go far, making you a guiding star for all. In your strong hands, the server stays bright, not fall to dark.
staff_statistics.level_8_description: You walk line between light and dark, sense chaos before it erupts. Quick freezes and strong kicks show your care for peace, no mercy for threats. Your subtlety and might work together so all in your land live in harmony.
staff_statistics.level_9_description: Through many fights you grew strong beyond normal. You blend smart plan with a strict code. Trolls and troublemakers vanish in your wake, every ban or mute a fair strike of justice. In this high post, your work shows the realmâ€™s unbreakable resilience.
